maintext: A volatile Republican primary features a former congressman, Lou Barletta; Bill McSwain, a former U.S. attorney appointed by President Donald J. Trump; David White, a steamfitter-turned-business-owner; and Doug Mastriano, a state lawmaker who has been an outspoken purveyor of false conspiracy theories about the 2020 election. Read more
